    "description": "　　《破阵》是一款极简主义风格的古代战术策略游戏。你将使用至少16名风格迥异的英雄角色，挑战超过160个关卡，独自对抗各种有趣的战术阵型。<br><br>　　你控制着独自行动的英雄武将，对抗一整支古代军队。在游戏中，你需要分析形势、规划英雄路线、选择突破口并在战术规划中达成关卡目标，并欣赏英雄的战斗演出。<br><br>　　完成游戏是一场有趣的智力考验，不过大多数关卡即使即兴发挥都可以轻松完成。执行完美的计划，悉心完成各种星级挑战，这才是更难掌握的技巧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D俯视视角，优雅而简约的战术玩法</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/dbe98460a6d33afb4e6c7ac30e350b13.poster.avif?t=1606808226\" width=628 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/dbe98460a6d33afb4e6c7ac30e350b13.webm?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/dbe98460a6d33afb4e6c7ac30e350b13.mp4?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　纯2D俯视视角+棋盘格战场，使战术规划更为直观。<br>　　利用风格迥异的战术，抽丝剥茧般地瓦解各式各样的敌军阵型。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爽快的战斗演出动画</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/4082dc8641577dfd5625370b060e150f.poster.avif?t=1606808226\" width=628 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/4082dc8641577dfd5625370b060e150f.webm?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/4082dc8641577dfd5625370b060e150f.mp4?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　战术规划完成后，游戏将进行一场酣畅淋漓的胜利演出。<br>　　享受骁勇的英雄为你带来的杀戮表演吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >极简主义风格的视觉设计</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/6db1b419c0a14f6bd550dae3eab54a9c.poster.avif?t=1606808226\" width=628 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/6db1b419c0a14f6bd550dae3eab54a9c.webm?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/6db1b419c0a14f6bd550dae3eab54a9c.mp4?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　极具风格的极简主义英雄和士兵，为您带来与众不同的视觉体验。<br>　　超过9种特殊兵种，16个可用英雄角色及其配套关卡。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的系列关卡</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/9ae493dcfbda31cde5c9ec621f24e990.poster.avif?t=1606808226\" width=628 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/9ae493dcfbda31cde5c9ec621f24e990.webm?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462220/extras/9ae493dcfbda31cde5c9ec621f24e990.mp4?t=1606808226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　　16个可用英雄角色，每个英雄都有一系列精心设计的专属关卡。<br>　　超过160个战斗关卡，每一个都极具挑战。",
